<%
  title "捐款"
  description "Pokrex 是一个免费的在线计划扑克工具，为了为广大用户继续提供服务，你可以通过 Paypal，微信或者支付宝向我付款。"
%>
<div class="row donate">
  <div class="col-xs-2 col-md-2"></div>
  <div class="col-xs-8 col-md-8 main">
    <h1>感谢你的捐款！</h1>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>❤️<a href="https://www.paypal.me/hlcfan" target="_blank">通过 Paypal 捐款</a></h3>
        <a href="https://www.paypal.me/hlcfan" target="_blank"><%= image_tag "paypal.jpg", size: "200x200" %></a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>💚微信收款码</h3>
        <%= image_tag "wechat.jpg", size: "200x200" %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>💙支付宝收款码</h3>
        <%= image_tag "alipay.jpg", size: "200x200" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="line-spliter">
        <span><b>👉名人堂👈</b></span>
      </div>
      <table class="table table-triped table-hover">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>#</th>
            <th>Name</th>
            <th>Amount</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% @donations.each_with_index do |donation, index| %>
            <tr>
              <th scope="row"><%= index %></th>
              <td><%= donation[:name] %></td>
              <td><%= donation[:amount] %></td>
            </tr>
          <% end %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <div class="col-md-11 col-md-offset-0">
        <blockquote>
          <p>
            I know you haven't made your mind up yet<br/>
            but I would never do you wrong<br/>
            I've known it from the moment that we met<br/>
            no doubt in my mind where you belong
          </p>
          <footer>Bob Dylan</footer>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-2 col-md-2"></div>
</div>
